---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="dayGLANCE"
  description="dayGLANCE is a calm daily planner for iOS, Android, and macOS. Morning intentions, daily notes, evening reflection—all in one quiet place."
>
  <article class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="mb-10 font-sans text-sm text-glance-dim" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-glance-muted transition-colors">GLANCE Apps</a>
      <span class="mx-2">/</span>
      <span class="text-glance-muted">dayGLANCE</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <div>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold leading-none mb-4">
          <span class="text-glance-muted font-medium">day</span><span class="text-glance-accent tracking-wider font-bold">GLANCE</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-glance-muted font-serif italic mb-8">
          Your day, at a glance.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-glance-muted font-serif text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          <p>
            dayGLANCE is a daily planner built around the idea that structure
            and stillness aren't opposites. Set a clear intention each morning,
            capture what comes up throughout the day, and end with a moment of
            reflection.
          </p>
          <p>
            No kanban boards. No recurring tasks cascading into the future.
            Just today—held simply and clearly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          {/* TODO: replace href with Play Store listing URL once published */}
          <a
            href="#"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="Get it on Google Play"
          >
            <img
              src="https://play.google.com/intl/en_us/badges/static/images/badges/en_badge_web_generic.png"
              alt="Get it on Google Play"
              width="155"
              height="60"
              class="h-[72px] w-auto"
            />
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://dayglance.app"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted hover:text-glance-accent transition-colors duration-150"
          >
            Visit dayglance.app →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-5">
            What it does
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4 font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-glance-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Morning intention</strong> — One clear thing to focus on today.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-glance-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Daily notes</strong> — A quiet space for thoughts, tasks, and whatever matters.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-glance-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Evening reflection</strong> — A gentle nudge to close the day with intention.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-glance-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Calendar aware</strong> — See what's on your schedule at a glance.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-4">
            Platforms
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted">Web · Android · macOS · Windows · Linux · iOS (soon)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-10 section-rule">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-6">
        Open Source
      </h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">
        dayGLANCE is open source under the MIT License. Self-host the web app,
        build from source, or audit the code. Purchases on the app stores support
        continued development.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/krelltunez/dayGLANCE"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-sans text-glance-accent link-underline"
      >
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" class="shrink-0 opacity-75">
          <path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/>
        </svg>
        View on GitHub →
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-10 section-rule">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-6">
        Privacy
      </h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">
        dayGLANCE stores all your data locally on your device. No account
        required. No data leaves your device without your direction. Your data
        remains yours.
      </p>
      <a href="/privacy" class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-accent link-underline">
        Privacy policy →
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
